title: Stone Maze
description: This maze takes place deeper within Earth's crust, and the enemies are stronger yet.

data.text: The maze is smaller than the last, however will prove to be a greater challenge for you. The monsters here are greater in number, as well as in strength. You will need to remain vigilant at all times. Once again, there is an SMG hidden somewhere in the maze for you. I strongly recommend searching thoroughly for it.

If you've made it this far then I applaud your bravery, however it isn't over yet. In the cave beyond lies Ginormous Gerry, the giant gorilla that has been trapped in the rocky cave floor. You must kill him before he pounds you to death with his two great fists. This fight will be much harder than the last one, while it may be possible to kill the gorilla with only your sidearm, I would go so far as to recommend going back into the maze to find the SMG if you don't have it now.
